                                        <span class="text-size-14 text-mr">The best approach to architecture building town planning recognizes the importance of integration and synergy between these disciplines. It involves thoughtful consideration of the overall urban fabric and the specific needs of the community. Architects, in collaboration with town planners, contribute their expertise to create buildings that are not only visually pleasing but also respond to the social, cultural, and environmental context.</span><br /><br />
